Posts.Content: May 7, 2006 02:39AM peejay wrote: Julie - Starting the very first chemo I would wake up completely soaked a couple of nights. It still happens, but mostly I just get really really hot in the face, then my whole head, and it spreads all over until I throw off all the blankets. Some night it drives my hubby crazy. I haven't gotten a period since I started chemo either, so I wonder if this is going to be menopause for me... I'm only 38, but it's possible the onc said.
